[gd_scene load_steps=52 format=3]

; MOUNTAIN — Climb the Peak.
; Tiers: forested base + cave / mid-tier lodge plateau / windy ridge + summit.
; Routes: skill-gate wall (wall-kick/long-jump) OR spiral ramp around the back.
; Secrets: cave shrine (1up + 2 red coins), wing-cap in tree leaves,
;   breakable-rock crevasse, rail-slide shortcut summit -> mid.
; Enemies: 7 goomba, 4 koopa, 2 bobomb, 3 cuttlefish, 1 bobomb buddy.
; Content: 30 yellow coins, 8 red coins, 2 stars, 2 1-ups, 1 wing cap.
; Player: ~1.5m penguin. Spawn near base facing uphill (-Z).

